$transitionBase: 250ms ease;
$transitionSlow: 400ms ease;
```

**Breakpoints:**
```scss
$bpMobile: 480px;    $bpTablet: 768px;
$bpDesktop: 1024px;  $bpWide: 1280px;
```

**Layout Constants:**
```scss
$navbarHeight: 64px;
$sidebarWidth: 280px;
$maxWidth: 1200px;
```

---

### 8. KEY SCSS MIXINS (_mixins.scss)

```scss
// Media queries
@mixin mobile { @media (max-width: $bpMobile) { @content; } }
@mixin tablet { @media (max-width: $bpTablet) { @content; } }
@mixin tabletUp { @media (min-width: ($bpTablet + 1)) { @content; } }
@mixin desktop { @media (min-width: $bpDesktop) { @content; } }
@mixin wide { @media (min-width: $bpWide) { @content; } }

// Glass morphism
@mixin glass {
  background: $glassBg;
  backdrop-filter: blur($glassBlur);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur($glassBlur);
  border: 1px solid $glassBorder;
}

// Text truncation
@mixin truncate($lines: 1) {
  @if $lines == 1 {
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
    white-space: nowrap;
  } @else {
    display: -webkit-box;
    -webkit-line-clamp: $lines;
    -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
}

// Custom scrollbar
@mixin customScrollbar {
  &::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; }
  &::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
    background: $textMuted;
    border-radius: $radiusFull;
  }
}

// Container max-width wrapper
@mixin container {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: $maxWidth;  // 1200px
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 $space6;  // 24px sides
  @include tablet { padding: 0 $space4; }  // 16px on tablet
}
```

---

### 9. INTEGRATION PATTERNS

**Chat activation flow:**
1. **From Candidate Profile:** Click "Contact Candidate" button
   - Calls `startConversation(candidateId, candidateName)` from ChatContext
   - Creates new conversation or opens existing one
   - Sidebar automatically scrolls to focus chat section

2. **From Chat Panel:** Click conversation item
   - Calls `openConversation(conversationId)`
   - Clears unread count
   - Shows detailed conversation view

3. **Sidebar visibility:** 
   - Desktop (1024px+): Always visible, sticky positioning
   - Tablet/Mobile: Drawer overlay from right with semi-transparent backdrop

---

### 10. ANIMATION PATTERNS

**Motion Library Setup:**
- Import: `import { motion, AnimatePresence } from "motion/react"`
- Common spring config: `{ type: "spring", stiffness: 300-400, damping: 25-30 }`
- Fast transitions: 150ms ease ($transitionFast)
- Page transitions use staggered child animations

**ChatPanel specific:**
- Conversation view: slides in from right (x: 30→0), spring animation
- List view: slides in from left (x: -30→0)
- Both use opacity transitions simultaneously

---

This comprehensive mapping shows how the chat system integrates into the sidebar, how pages are structured, and the complete design token system supporting theming and responsive behavior.

